    "Answers may vary depending on the wording of the question or the language used.",
    "Review and analyse the responses to consider different formulations.",
    "Use technical tools to verify that the model's responses are correct, especially in cases where the recommendations could have an important impact.",
    "Large language models can generate correct answers to questions, but they can also create fictional facts or alter information.",
